<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>12369</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>18063</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>汤姆去拿魔杖。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>18064</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>21631</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“可怜的玛丽公主。”他想，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>21632</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>24248</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“她善良又美丽。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>24249</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>28191</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我必须变出粉红莓来！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>28192</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>34929</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“猫咪？”汤姆叫道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>34930</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>38531</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>没有回答。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>38532</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>42570</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>汤姆拿起了魔杖。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>42571</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>46769</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“粉红莓！”他大叫。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>46770</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>57439</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>噗！一头粉红色的大象出现了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>57440</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>63630</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>噗！噗！噗！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>63631</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>68677</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>汤姆一次又一次地挥动着魔杖。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>68678</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>72890</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>德克冲进了实验室。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>72891</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>78446</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“粉红莓在哪里？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>78447</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>84188</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我，呃，我还要一点时间。”汤姆说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>84189</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>88385</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你这个傻瓜！”德克大叫，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>88386</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>91009</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“公主的病很严重！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>91010</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>94644</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我们现在就要！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>94645</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>98169</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>德克生气地瞪着汤姆。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>98170</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>100763</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我有个主意。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>100764</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>106863</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>有个传说，粉红莓生长在黑暗森林里。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>106864</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>109517</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>汤姆大吃一惊。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>109518</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>111707</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“黑暗森林？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>111708</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>113731</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>德克点点头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>113732</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>117790</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“说那里一年四季都有粉红莓，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>117791</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>121034</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>也许你可以找到。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>121035</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>125660</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>汤姆说：“但是......”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>125661</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>129767</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>德克把他从实验室里推了出去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>129768</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>132581</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“现在就去！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>132582</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>143307</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>汤姆走进了黑暗森林。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>143308</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>153593</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他路过了高高的树和弯弯的草丛。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>153594</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>164803</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他的靴子陷进了泥里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>164804</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>168443</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>嘶嘶！簌簌！咕咕！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>168444</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>172043</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>空中都是可怕的声音。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>172044</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>177052</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>就在这时，一只蝙蝠飞过了汤姆的头顶。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>177053</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>181579</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“啊！”他挥手赶走了蝙蝠。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>181580</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>184086</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哎呀！”汤姆大叫。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>184087</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>198379</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他的魔杖飞了起来，落到了泥里，越陷越深。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>